      "text": "**ChatCompletionResponse**(\n  finish_reason='content_filter',\n  message.content=refusal.human_message\n) + **ArcGuardEnvelope**(\n  blocked=True, blocked_phase='pre_process',\n  pre=ArcGuardPhase(action=block, refusal_code='jailbreak_strong'),\n  post=None\n)",
