    {
      "id": "u3_gap_dedup",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "⚠ GAP — no per-attacker dedup / rate-limit\nA bot hammering the endpoint generates one block log per request. No counter, no rolling window, no auto-throttle. Belongs in api middleware, not the pipeline.",
